ADMIT ONE! TICKET TO 'LUZ WRLD' AMUSEMENT PARKZ

Welcome to the main entrance of LUZ-WRLD, a fictional amusement park that will one day soon, manifest into a physical park. This first animation serves as your ticket of entry to the park(Z)!  
This ticket will be required to participate in all park activities and rideZ  
In addition to having a LUZ animation in your collection, this ticket will be eligible for future claims and rewards.
